Wings . Hyaline. Legs . Integument brownish. Vestiture greyish to yellowish. Ts coarsely serrate, with 6–7 oblique projections ( Fig. 103f ). Bp broad; pointed apically (
Fig. 103g
). Metasoma . L = 2,7–3,3mm ; W = 1,7–2,0mm. Integument reddish to brownish except the margins of T pallid brownish and pallid yellowish (usually T2–T4); T1 often (extensively) blackish; margins of T1–T4 extensively translucent. Apical hair bands on metasomal terga absent (sometimes they are weakly present on T3–T4). Prepygidial fimbria mostly yellowish. Metasomal terga as illustrated in Fig. 103d .
